{
  "stem": "6076.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I used to have a special two dresses made with short sleeves, because I could not wear long sleeves.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Every girl had short sleeves.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And I was crying to my mother.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I says, ma, I want to wear short sleeves.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "It's so hot.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "It's in the summer.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "They're all wearing shorts sleeves.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I don't want to be different than all the girls.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I'm not talking about the gentiles, about the Jewish girls.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And my mother says, [NON-ENGLISH], soon, when you come home, take off that dress and put it in the closet that Papa shouldn't see it.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "So I did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "But I was always sneaky.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "I always wanted to be on the modern side, because it pull me more to the modern side, always.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And-- and that's what I did.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And my mother used to give me a smile.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "She says, OK, do it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "But it was a gossip going around in our shtetl.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Because gossip was very, very-- it was gossip in the shtetl.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "Because one lived near each other.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "You could hear every knock from each other.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And if somebody walked on the street, you know, they would tell how she walked and how she dressed.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And everybody was gossiping about each other.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "Most of the people, the Jewish people, they did that in the smaller shtetls.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "In our house, we didn't gossip, because this was a sin, to gossip.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "My mother will say, sh!",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "Don't ever talk about nobody.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "My father, [INAUDIBLE], that was the biggest sin.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "You could never say that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "But most of the people, you know, in the town, they would gossip.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they will talk to the rabbi, to our rabbi in shtetl.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they will tell him that Solomon Szlomo's younger girl is wearing short sleeves to school.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
